 the left, as
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mbox{tak}_{K;w}\left(\frac{x}{2K}\right)=x+w\;\mbox{tak}_{K;w}\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset

for 
\begin_inset Formula $0\le x\le1$
\end_inset

